urdu transliteration text:
@HujjatELC
Bahar aane ko na khaime se Main Kehta Tum koHote Abbas a.s to takleef na Deta Tum koBanke Abbas a.s Mujhe zee pe bithado Zainab s.aApne Hathon se Kafan Mujhko pinhado Zainab s.a
By becoming Abbas, help me ride over the saddle

@HujjatELC
Qaid khane ki sambhalo yeh Amanat BibiGhod mein lo Ise Mazloom ho rukhsat BibiMera daman Meri Bacchi se churado Zainab s.aApne Hathon se Kafan Mujhko pinhado Zainab s.a
Get my shirt released from my daughters’ hand, Zainab
